cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper discusses the behavior and decision-making of learning machines, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The analysis is applied to tasks in computer vision (cs.CV) and arcade games, which further supports the inclusion of cs.CV. The paper also proposes a new method for characterizing and validating the behavior of nonlinear learning machines, which could fall under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL) or neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
